snippet.title: Resident Evil Origins Collection Trailer
snippet.description:
Witness the origins of the Resident Evil universe with the Resident Evil Origins Collection, coming as a physical disc product to PlayStation 4 and Xbox One starting January 19th, 2016 for $39.99. The Origins Collection gives you both the upcoming Resident Evil 0, as well as the highly well received Resident Evil, which released as a digital download earlier in 2015.
